.Dd June 24, 2026
.Dt X11DND_XT_CANCEL_DRAG 3
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm x11dnd_xt_cancel_drag
.Nd cancel the active Xt drag operation
.Sh LIBRARY
.Lb libx11dnd
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.In x11dnd_xt.h
.Ft void
.Fn x11dnd_xt_cancel_drag "void"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Fn x11dnd_xt_cancel_drag
cancels the active drag started by
.Xr x11dnd_xt_start_drag 3 .
It removes the Xt work proc and event handler, then calls
.Xr x11dnd_cancel_drag 3
on the active source session.
.Pp
This function is also called automatically when the ESC key is pressed
during a drag if the
.Dv X11DND_ICON_CANCEL_ESC
flag was set in the
.Vt X11DndDragIcon
configuration.
.Sh RETURN VALUES
None.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr x11dnd_xt_start_drag 3 ,
.Xr x11dnd_cancel_drag 3 ,
.Xr x11dnd 3
